The Alex Jones Show

Friday January 02, 2009.

Alex kicks off the New Year.  Guests include Bob Chapman of the International Forecaster who will talk about the economy and Robert Wanek, the student who had his 9/11 truth t-shirt censored in the high school yearbook.  Alex also discusses the important issues of the day and takes your calls.

Hour-1: News and Rants
Hour-2: Bob Chapman
Hour-3: Open Lines with Bob Chapman
Hour-4: Robert Wanek
Hour-5: Robert Wanek and massive rants
